short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Free helper tool for SEOs. Easily check a site's position for a given keyword in Google.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows you to match a keyword search with a website.  It helps to find the ranking on a targeted version of Google. 

Simple, instantaneous and very effective.

In case of blocking, be sure to check the result of the search list after captcha to resolve it.

If your country is missing from the Google list, leave us a comment.

And don't forget to evaluate the extension, it will increase our visibility and the popularity of the extension.

Have fun!
